          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "In the light of the king’s face is life, And his favor is like a cloud of the latter rain. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "In the light of the king’s face is life, And his favor is like a cloud of the latter rain."
